[1] Lacoste, P. "Solution of Maxwell equation in axisymmetric geometry by Fourier series decompostion and by use of H (rot) conforming finite element." Numerische Mathematik 84.4 (2000): 577-609.\
[2] Belhachmi, Z, et al. "A truncated Fourier/finite element discretization of the Stokes equations in an axisymmetric domain." Mathematical Models and Methods in Applied Sciences 16.02 (2006): 233-263.\
[3] Albert, CG, et al. "A two-dimensional vector potential formulation for periodic magnetostatic fields in symmetric domains", Manuscript in preparation (2016).\
[4] Albert, CG, et al. "Kinetic modeling of 3D equilibria in a tokamak", JPCS / Varenna-Lausanne Workshop on Theory of Fusion Plasmas (forthcoming, 2016).}